description         Text::Fuzzy - Partial string matching using edit distances

long_description    This module calculates edit distances between words, and \
                    searches arrays and files to find the nearest entry by \
                    edit distance. It handles both byte strings and \
                    character strings (strings containing Unicode), treating \
                    each Unicode character as a single entity.

